    {
      "id": "detailed_4_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_4",
      "description": "Well-kept older vehicle in good overall condition and priced accordingly. It presents nicely for its age, with expected minor cosmetic wear such as small exterior blemishes, light age-related wear to trim and paint, and a clean, used but respectable interior. It appears to have been maintained better than a typical older budget car and should suit a buyer looking for a solid driver rather than a project or a fully restored example. Not perfect and not showroom-level, but a good, honest car that shows well and should meet expectations for a vehicle in this condition.",
