    },
    {
      "id": "optimistic_8_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_8",
      "description": "Exceptionally clean, beautifully kept vehicle in mint condition and ready to drive. It shows extremely well, has clearly been very well cared for, and only shows the lightest signs of normal use. A standout example for anyone looking for a top-condition car at a fair market price.",
