    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Budget-friendly and straightforward, this vehicle is a practical option for anyone seeking affordable transportation without the premium price tag. It presents as a well-used car with character, but it still offers solid everyday utility and strong value for the money. A smart choice for a commuter, first-time buyer, or someone looking for an inexpensive extra vehicle.",
