      "timestep_posted": 10
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Looking for an affordable car with plenty of life left for the right person? This one isn\u2019t perfect, but it\u2019s an honest, budget-friendly option that could make a great runaround, project, or first car for someone handy. It has the kind of straightforward charm that makes it easy to appreciate, and at this price point, it\u2019s a solid chance to get into a car without spending big. If you want something inexpensive and see the value in a car with potential, this one is well worth a look.",
      "price": 4950.0,
