      "description": "Reliable platform with solid bones and plenty of life left for the next owner. Engine starts up, transmission engages, and it moves out well enough to serve as a practical commuter, shop runner, or project build. Not a show car, but the core mechanical package is there, with straightforward serviceability and the kind of durable engineering enthusiasts appreciate. A good opportunity for someone who wants affordable transportation with upside for improvement.",
